snippet.title: Poison Baby | Thamma | Malaika A, Ayushmann K, Rashmika M | Sachin-Jigar,Jasmine S, Divya, Amitabh B
snippet.description:
Before the poison hits your veins, let the beat sink in.
#PoisonBaby Out Now!

On 21st October, love turns lethal in #Thamma! üî•

üéß Listen to "Poison Baby" on:

‚ûü Spotify - https://open.spotify.com/track/4LI5shJ67j5pPhlw6VGZTS?si=2f7a2aaa69f54690
‚ûü YouTube Music - https://music.youtube.com/watch?v=2aetKpwNXfw&si=NCHjbk0GLSUsCnNP
‚ûü Amazon Music - https://music.amazon.com/tracks/B0FVXNYMNS?marketplaceId=A3K6Y4MI8GDYMT&musicTerritory=IN&ref=dm_sh_txnp1i5ESury0vaO5H2IKnFwe
‚ûü Apple Music - https://music.apple.com/us/song/poison-baby-from-thamma/1845813900

üé¨ Do the hookstep of #PoisonBaby on:
‚ûü Reels - https://www.instagram.com/reels/audio/1305899311000244/?igsh=MWM5aG8xOTBnOWE0

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
üéß  Audio Credits

üé∂ Music : Sachin-Jigar
üé§ Singer : Jasmine Sandlas, Sachin-Jigar, Divya Kumar
‚ûü Lyrics : Amitabh Bhattacharya  
‚ûü Programmed & Arranged -Sachin- Jigar, Abhishek Singh @ White Noise Collectives
‚ûü Backing Vocals - Sumonto Mukherjee, Abhishek Singh, Noor Parmar, Hitesh Purani
‚ûü Music Production Head : Romil Ved
‚ûü Electric Guitars - Noor Parmar @ White Noise Collectives 
‚ûü Recording Engineer - Susmeet Rewaskar @ White Noise Collectives
‚ûü Mixed & Mastered : Eric Pillai @ FSOB
‚ûü Assistant Mixing Engineer - Michael Edwin Pillai

üé¨ Video Credits

‚ûü Cast: Ayushmann Khurrana, Rashmika Mandanna, Paresh Rawal, Nawazuddin Siddiqui, Faisal Malik, Rachit Singh
‚ûü Produced By: Dinesh Vijan, Amar Kaushik
‚ûü Directed By: Aditya Sarpotdar
‚ûü Co-Producers: Sharada Karki Jalota, Pooja Prem Patheja
‚ûü Director of Photography: Jishnu Bhattacharjee
‚ûü Music / Background Score: Sachin‚ÄìJigar
‚ûü Lyrics: Amitabh Bhattacharya
‚ûü Costume Designer: Sheetal Iqbal Sharma
‚ûü Director of Choreography: Sekhar Master
‚ûü Publicity Design: Himanshu & Rahul Nanda (H-One)


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
üìù Lyrics

SHER

MALE 
Hum dil ke bure nahin
Bas ek kharaabi hai
Aadat se nahin
Hum shauq se sharaabi hain


MUKHDA 

FEMALE 
(Kya hoga saaqiyon ka jo hum
Peena chhod dein) √ó2

Peena chhodne se behtar hai
Jeena chhod dein

(Gin'ne padein gilaas toh
Ginti na chhod dein) √ó2

Peena chhodne se behtar hai
Jeena chhod dein

CHORUS
Teri aankhein ..Poison baby
Baatein ..Poison baby
Nakhre tere lazeez hai

Tere latke.. poison baby
Jhatke.. poison baby
Har sitam bhi azeez hai

ANTARA
FEMALE 
Maarte hi chuski
Pyaale se som ras ki
Umr ho gayi kam
Maano kayi baras ki

Pee hi jab liya toh
Baat karke vo dikha dein
Jo nahi thi peene se
Pehle apne bas ki

CHORUS
Pehle apne bas ki

FEMALE
(Toke jo uske sar pe
Botan na phod dein) √ó2

Peena chhodne se behtar hai
Jeena chhod dein..

(Kya hoga saaqiyon ka jo hum
Peena chhod dein) √ó2

Peena chhodne se behtar hai
Jeena chhod dein

CHORUS
Teri aankhein ..Poison baby
Baatein ..Poison baby
Nakhre tere lazeez hai

Tere latke.. poison baby
Jhatke.. poison baby
Har sitam bhi azeez hai


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

snippet.title: [Hindi] BMSD 2025 | Grand Finals | Day 3
snippet.description:
The Top 8 teams from the Semi Finals and Top 8 teams from the Survival Stage are set to battle across 3 intense days of high-stakes BGMI action. The competition is fierce, the pressure is real, and only one team will rise above the rest.

The team that finishes at the top of the leaderboard will earn a slot at the global stage, as the journey to go Beyond Limits reaches its peak!

Madkings

snippet.title: Andhra King Taluka Teaser | Ram Pothineni | Upendra | Mahesh Babu P | Bhagyashri Borse

Presenting the Energetic teaser of #AndhraKingTaluka 

Andhra King Taluka - A BIOPIC OF A FAN is a Telugu Film starring Ram Pothineni, Upendra and Bhagyashri Borse. The film is written and directed by Mahesh Babu P and produced by Naveen Yerneni, Y. Ravi Shankar under Mythri Movie Makers. Music is by Vivek & Mervin. The film brings untold emotions between a fan and a superstar onto the big screens on 28th November worldwide.

snippet.description:

Presenting the lyrical of ''Onde Ondu Sala'' from the movie ''The Devil'' starring Challenging Star Darshan, Rachana Rai and others. Shri Jaimatha Combines, in association with Saregama a Yoodlee Films, presents the much-awaited film The Devil. 

Song Credits:

Music Composed, Arranged & Programmed by: B. Ajaneesh Loknath
Singers: Kapil Kapilan, Chinmayi Sripada
Lyrics: Pramod Maravanthe
Choreographer: Santhu Master

Flute: Kiran

PRO: Sudhindra Venkatesh
Digital PR: Pavan Venkatesh

(Male)
Onde Ondu Sala Sothu Bide Nee
Onde Ondu Maathu Aadade
Bendu Bendu Ninna Daahadolage
Noora Ondu Aase Moodide......

(Female)
Modalu Modalene
Edeya Kenakone
Enidu Arivaagadu
Nee Preethi Maado Pariye.....
Sulive Kodadene
Sulige Nadesone
Maimana Sudutha Ide
Onde Ondu Sala
Ninna Kanna Jwaalaamukhige......

(Female)
Mareyaadaru Marethodaru
Matthe Baruve Matthu tharuve 
Koralanchige Kathe Helalu
Mutthuugalane Munde Biduve..... Ideke......

(Male)
Dhaga Dhageya Thanda
Aa Nageyu Ninde
Jagamagiso Neenu
Bekeega Nangene....
Gara Garane Thirugide
Ninna Amaleri
Ghama Ghamiso Ee Dehaanu Nangene.....

(Male)
Onde Ondu Sala Sothu Bide Nee
Onde Ondu Maathu Aadade
Naane Bandu Ninna Bandhisidaru
Neene Nanna Bandhi Maadide.....

(Female)
Kodalaare Kodalaare
Nannandavanu Ninage Heege
Badalaagu Badalaagu
Nanna Manave Solo Haage....

(Male)
Bara Sidilu Thande
Naa Nadugo Hage
Ee Badalavanege
Roovaari Neenene....
Gara Garane Thirugide
Ninna Amaleri
Ghama Ghamiso Ee Dehaanu Nangene.....

(Male)
Onde Ondu Sala Sothu Bide Nee
Onde Ondu Maathu Aadade
Bandu Nanna Ede Kaadinolage
Kaadgicchu Hacchi Kaadide......

snippet.description:
Step into the world of resonant romance with Alka Yagnik's enchanting voice in the unforgettable track 'Ikrar Ho Na Jaye' from the movie Zinda Dil. This soulful melody from the early 2000s is sure to rekindle the season of love in your hearts. Let the silky timbre of Alka Yagnik, the queen of romantic numbers, transport you to an era where music was emotionally stirring and purely heartfelt. Dive deep into the pool of nostalgia and let the magic of the song wrap you in its romantic embrace.
